# Test Cases – Login Module

| ID      | Title                                | Precondition                     | Steps                                                                 | Expected result                                                    |
|---------|--------------------------------------|----------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------|
| TC_LOGIN_001 | Successful login with valid data | User account exists, is active   | 1. Open login page<br>2. Enter valid email<br>3. Enter valid password<br>4. Click "Login" | User is redirected to dashboard/home page.                        |
| TC_LOGIN_002 | Login with invalid password     | User account exists              | 1. Open login page<br>2. Enter valid email<br>3. Enter invalid password<br>4. Click "Login" | Login is rejected, meaningful error message is shown.             |
| TC_LOGIN_003 | Empty email and password        | –                                | 1. Open login page<br>2. Leave email and password empty<br>3. Click "Login" | Form is not submitted, validation messages are shown.             |
| TC_LOGIN_004 | Invalid email format            | –                                | 1. Open login page<br>2. Enter "user@" as email<br>3. Enter any password<br>4. Click "Login" | Validation error for email format is displayed.                   |
| TC_LOGIN_005 | Logout                           | User is logged in                | 1. Click "Logout" button<br>2. Try to open a protected page via URL | User is redirected to login page, protected page is not accessible. |
